{
  "id": "136",
  "title": "圆形花瓣环",
  "description": "画 8 个空心圆排成一圈，形成花瓣环。\n\n**绘图要求：**\n- 线条粗细：2\n- 循环 8 次\n- 每次：\n  - 颜色 `i+1`\n  - 抬笔前进 55 步，落笔\n  - 画空心圆半径 25（`pen.o(25)`）\n  - 抬笔返回（bk(55)），落笔\n  - 右转 45°",
  "difficulty": "easy",
  "tags": [
    "循环",
    "圆",
    "颜色",
    "对称",
    "抬笔落笔"
  ],
  "starterCode": "pen.size(2);\nfor(int i=0; i<8; i++){\n    pen.c(i+1);\n    pen.up().fd(55).down();\n    pen.o(25);\n    pen.up().bk(55).down();\n    pen.rt(45);\n}\n",
  "solution": "pen.size(2);\nfor(int i=0; i<8; i++){\n    pen.c(i+1);\n    pen.up().fd(55).down();\n    pen.o(25);\n    pen.up().bk(55).down();\n    pen.rt(45);\n}",
  "hint": "8个圆每隔45°（360÷8）排一个；pen.o(r) 以当前位置为圆心画圆。",
  "constraints": "必须使用 for 循环",
